      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project or a budget-friendly way to get around? This vehicle is in poor condition and will definitely need some mechanical and cosmetic TLC, but it offers a great opportunity for someone handy or looking for a fixer-upper! It\u2019s an honest car at a price that leaves you plenty of room to make it your own.",
