    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project car or a source for parts. The engine has significant performance issues, including a persistent oil leak and a rough idle, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, the body shows heavy rust in several areas, significant dents, and peeling clear coat. The interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery and several non-functional electronic components. Please expect that this vehicle will require substantial mechanical repairs and bodywork to be roadworthy again.",
